The initial release of this management information module.

usdAccountingAgent.contactinfo: Unisphere Networks, Inc. Postal: 10 Technology Park Drive Westford, MA 01886 USA Tel: +1 978 589 5800 E-mail: mib@UnisphereNetworks.com
usdAccountingAgent.description: The agent capabilities definitions for the Accounting component of the SNMP agent in the Unisphere Routing Switch family of products.

usdAccountingAgentV1.name: usdAccountingAgentV1
usdAccountingAgentV1.productrelease:
Version 1 of the Accounting component of the Unisphere Routing Switch
        SNMP agent.  This version of the Accounting component was supported in
        the Unisphere RX 2.0 thru 3.1 system releases.
usdAccountingAgentV1.description: The MIBs supported by the SNMP agent for the Accounting application in the Unisphere Routing Switch. These capabilities became obsolete when the usdAcctngSelectionSubtreeType object was deprecated.

usdAccountingAgentV2.name: usdAccountingAgentV2
usdAccountingAgentV2.productrelease:
Version 2 of the Accounting component of the Unisphere Routing Switch
        SNMP agent.  This version of the Accounting component wass supported in
        the Unisphere RX 3.2 thru 3.x system releases.
usdAccountingAgentV2.description: The MIBs supported by the SNMP agent for the Accounting application in the Unisphere Routing Switch. These capabilities became obsolete when support was added to the Unisphere-Data-ACCOUNTING-MIB for selection policy name and type objects.

usdAccountingAgentV3.name: usdAccountingAgentV3
usdAccountingAgentV3.productrelease:
Version 3 of the Accounting component of the Unisphere Routing Switch
        SNMP agent.  This version of the Accounting component is supported in
        the Unisphere RX 4.0 and subsequent system releases.
usdAccountingAgentV3.description: The MIBs supported by the SNMP agent for the Accounting application in the Unisphere Routing Switch.
